@chapter Limitations
There are currently some known limitations when using Octave.app. These limitations need not to be reported on an Octave mailing list. But if you find other bugs or other limitations in the Octave.app respectively Octave then please report them to @email{octave-dev@@lists.sourceforge.net}.

